The paper deals with understanding visual ads, which involves image analysis and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses attention mechanisms and co-attention, which are common techniques in natural language processing, suggesting that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper deals with multimodal representations, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves learning and optimization, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves ranking and retrieval, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
